* meta.dts
* Canonical entry point for metadata tooling in the staged/runtime tree.
*
* This is intentionally non-destructive:
*   - it activates the metadata lane
*   - it loads the current metadata workspace
*   - it points maintainers at the schema-generation scripts under data\meta
*
* To create or refresh the system metadata schema, run:
*   DO meta\SYSTEM_METADATA_SCHEMA_v1

DO metadata
WORKSPACE LOAD metadata

ECHO ===== META TOOLING READY =====
ECHO Metadata workspace is active.
ECHO Tool scripts live under data\meta.
ECHO To create or refresh the catalog schema:
ECHO   DO meta\SYSTEM_METADATA_SCHEMA_v1
ECHO =================================
